snippet.title: Punch Club 2: The Iron Fist – Official DLC Reveal Trailer | tinyBuild Connect 2024
snippet.description:
The first DLC for Punch Club 2: Fast Forward is coming in July 2024 - Get ready for the Iron Fist expansion, where you’ll be facing off in the Robot League! So strap on your gloves, start your training and get ready for the fight of a lifetime!

#IGN #Gaming
